#. plugin:mailchimp:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "- **Dashboard**: View all your MailChimp lists with subscriber statistics\n"
"- **List Maintenance**: Identify people in MailChimp but not in CRM, and vice versa\n"
"- **Contact Integration**: View MailChimp subscription status on Person and Family pages\n"
"- **Automatic Sync**: Hooks into person/family updates to keep MailChimp in sync"
msgstr "- **Dasbor**: Lihat semua daftar MailChimp Anda beserta statistik pelanggan\n"
"- **Pemeliharaan Daftar**: Identifikasi orang yang ada di MailChimp tapi tidak di CRM, dan sebaliknya\n"
"- **Integrasi Kontak**: Lihat status langganan MailChimp di halaman Orang dan Keluarga\n"
"- **Sinkronisasi Otomatis**: Terhubung ke pembaruan orang/keluarga untuk menjaga MailChimp tetap sinkron"

#. plugin:vonage:section:1:content
#: 
msgid "1. Create a Vonage account at https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-up (new accounts include free trial credit)\n"
"2. Find your API Key and API Secret on the Vonage Dashboard homepage\n"
"3. Go to Numbers > Buy Numbers and purchase a number with SMS capability\n"
"4. Note the number in E.164 format (e.g., +14155551234)\n"
"5. In ChurchCRM, enable the Vonage SMS plugin and enter your credentials"
msgstr "1. Buat akun Vonage di https://dashboard.nexmo.com/sign-up (akun baru termasuk kredit uji coba gratis)\n"
"2. Temukan API Key dan API Secret Anda di beranda Dasbor Vonage\n"
"3. Pergi ke Nomor > Beli Nomor dan beli nomor dengan kemampuan SMS\n"
"4. Catat nomor dalam format E.164 (mis., +14155551234)\n"
"5. Di ChurchCRM, aktifkan plugin Vonage SMS dan masukkan kredensial Anda"

#. plugin:google-analytics:section:0:content
#: 
msgid "1. Go to Google Analytics (analytics.google.com)\n"
"2. Create a property or select an existing one\n"
"3. Go to Admin → Data Streams → Web\n"
"4. Copy the Measurement ID (starts with G-)"
msgstr "1. Buka Google Analytics (analytics.google.com)\n"
"2. Buat properti atau pilih yang sudah ada\n"
"3. Pergi ke Admin → Aliran Data → Web\n"
"4. Salin ID Pengukuran (dimulai dengan G-)"

#. plugin:openlp:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "1. Install OpenLP 3.0 or later on your presentation computer\n"
"2. Enable the Remote plugin in OpenLP (Settings → Configure OpenLP → Plugins)\n"
"3. Enable the Alerts plugin in OpenLP for alert display support\n"
"4. Note the IP address of the OpenLP computer\n"
"5. Enter the server URL in the format: http://IP_ADDRESS:4316\n"
"6. If you've configured authentication in OpenLP, enter the username and password"
msgstr "1. Instal OpenLP 3.0 atau lebih baru di komputer presentasi Anda\n"
"2. Aktifkan plugin Remote di OpenLP (Pengaturan → Konfigurasikan OpenLP → Plugin)\n"
"3. Aktifkan plugin Alerts di OpenLP untuk dukungan tampilan peringatan\n"
"4. Catat alamat IP komputer OpenLP\n"
"5. Masukkan URL server dalam format: http://IP_ADDRESS:4316\n"
"6. Jika Anda telah mengonfigurasi autentikasi di OpenLP, masukkan nama pengguna dan kata sandi"

#. plugin:mailchimp:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "Access the MailChimp Dashboard from the Email menu. The dashboard shows:\n"
"\n"
"- Member count for each list\n"
"- Campaign statistics\n"
"- Unsubscribe counts\n"
"- List maintenance tools"
msgstr "Akses Dasbor MailChimp dari menu Email. Dasbor menampilkan:\n"
"\n"
"- Jumlah anggota untuk setiap daftar\n"
"- Statistik kampanye\n"
"- Jumlah berhenti berlangganan\n"
"- Alat pemeliharaan daftar"

#. plugin:custom-links:section:1:title
#: 
msgid "Adding Links"
msgstr "Menambahkan Tautan"

#. plugin:custom-links:section:2:content
#: 
msgid "All configured links are shown in a table. You can:\n"
"- View the link name and URL\n"
"- Click the URL to test it opens correctly\n"
"- Delete links you no longer need\n"
"\n"
"Links appear in the order they were added in the navigation menu."
msgstr "Semua tautan yang dikonfigurasi ditampilkan dalam tabel. Anda dapat:\n"
"- Melihat nama tautan dan URL\n"
"- Klik URL untuk menguji apakah terbuka dengan benar\n"
"- Hapus tautan yang tidak lagi diperlukan\n"
"\n"
"Tautan muncul sesuai urutan penambahannya di menu navigasi."

#: 
msgid "Allow Pre-release Upgrades"
msgstr "Izinkan Peningkatan Versi Pra-rilis"

#: 
msgid "Allow recording of non-tax-deductible payments in the finance module"
msgstr "Izinkan pencatatan pembayaran yang tidak dapat dikurangi pajak di modul keuangan"

#: 
msgid "Allow scanned check images to be attached to deposit records"
msgstr "Izinkan gambar cek yang dipindai dilampirkan ke catatan setoran"

#: 
msgid "Allow system upgrades to releases marked as 'pre release' on GitHub"
msgstr "Izinkan peningkatan sistem ke rilis yang ditandai sebagai 'pra rilis' di GitHub"

#: 
msgid "Allow unauthenticated access to calendar events via public HTML, ICS, and JSON URLs. Required for sharing calendars with external apps."
msgstr "Izinkan akses tidak terautentikasi ke acara kalender melalui URL HTML, ICS, dan JSON publik. Diperlukan untuk berbagi kalender dengan aplikasi eksternal."

#: 
msgid "Allow visitors to create their own family record via the self-registration page"
msgstr "Izinkan pengunjung membuat catatan keluarga mereka sendiri melalui halaman pendaftaran mandiri"

#: 
msgid "Allow visitors to self-register as new families."
msgstr "Izinkan pengunjung mendaftar sendiri sebagai keluarga baru."

#. plugin:external-backup:section:5:content
#: 
msgid "Any WebDAV-compatible service works with this plugin:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (recommended)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (with WebDAV)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx with WebDAV module\n"
"\n"
"Note: Some services require app-specific passwords for WebDAV access."
msgstr "Layanan apa pun yang kompatibel dengan WebDAV bekerja dengan plugin ini:\n"
"\n"
"- Nextcloud (direkomendasikan)\n"
"- ownCloud\n"
"- Synology NAS\n"
"- QNAP NAS\n"
"- Box.com (dengan WebDAV)\n"
"- Apache mod_dav\n"
"- nginx dengan modul WebDAV\n"
"\n"
"Catatan: Beberapa layanan memerlukan kata sandi khusus aplikasi untuk akses WebDAV."

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:title
#: 
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Autentikasi"

#. plugin:openlp:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Authentication is required for API v2 if you've enabled it in OpenLP's Remote plugin settings. The plugin uses HTTP Basic Authentication. Most local network setups don't require authentication, but it's recommended for security."
msgstr "Autentikasi diperlukan untuk API v2 jika Anda telah mengaktifkannya di pengaturan plugin Remote OpenLP. Plugin menggunakan Autentikasi Dasar HTTP. Sebagian besar pengaturan jaringan lokal tidak memerlukan autentikasi, tetapi direkomendasikan untuk keamanan."

#: 
msgid "Auto TLS"
msgstr "TLS Otomatis"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:2:title
#: 
msgid "Auto-Backup"
msgstr "Pencadangan Otomatis"

#: 
msgid "BCC All Mail To"
msgstr "BCC Semua Email Ke"

#. plugin:external-backup:section:4:content
#: 
msgid "Before relying on external backups, test your connection:\n"
"1. Go to Plugins > External Backup\n"
"2. Click 'Test WebDAV Connection'\n"
"3. Verify you see a success message\n"
"\n"
"Common issues:\n"
"- 401/403 errors: Check username and password\n"
"- Connection timeout: Verify the endpoint URL is correct\n"
"- Certificate errors: Ensure the WebDAV server has a valid SSL certificate"
msgstr "Sebelum mengandalkan pencadangan eksternal, uji koneksi Anda:\n"
"1. Pergi ke Plugin > Pencadangan Eksternal\n"
"2. Klik 'Uji Koneksi WebDAV'\n"
"3. Pastikan Anda melihat pesan sukses\n"
"\n"
"Masalah umum:\n"
"- Kesalahan 401/403: Periksa nama pengguna dan kata sandi\n"
"- Batas waktu koneksi: Pastikan URL endpoint sudah benar\n"
"- Kesalahan sertifikat: Pastikan server WebDAV memiliki sertifikat SSL yang valid"

